From c39e595aedd501bac4fd5879eed07a5f7d6a060c Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Tzachi Shaiovitch <tzachish1@gmail.com>
Date: Mon, 26 Jan 2026 18:41:28 +0200
Subject: [PATCH 06/22] feat(node-governance): Add node governance feature for
 controlling node access

- Add policy management (allow/block at global/project scope)
- Add category system for grouping nodes
- Add access request workflow with approval/rejection
- Integrate governance status in node creator
- Auto-disable blocked nodes in template imports
- Add 24 unit tests (16 controller + 8 service priority tests)
- Add E2E test suite (28 tests)
